title: Peyton Sawyer - A Hundred Songs To Save Your Life (OTH)
description:
Playlist inspired by the TV show character Peyton Sawyer from One Tree Hill. Her podcast, the songs she commented on the show, songs that played in her room helped me to chose the songs and the music supervisor of One Tree Hill, Lindsay! I hope you enjoy it!
